Hillsdown Holdings Plc &lt;HLDN.L> said itsChristie-Tyler Ltd unit would buy the European bedding makinginterests of Simmons Co U.S.A., Owned by Gulf and WesternIndustries Inc USA &lt;GW>, for 23 mln dlrs.    The acquisitions include &lt;Sleepeeze Ltd> in the U.K.,&lt;Compagnie Continentale Simmons SA> in France and &lt;CompagniaItaliana Simmons SpA> in Italy.    In 1986 the three businesses made pre-tax profit of around2.5 mln stg on sales of 39 mln stg. Net assets being acquiredcome to around nine mln stg.    Hillsdown shares were unchanged at 266p. REUTER&#3;